properties.Name: ShipmentMethod
properties.Description:
The method by which the shipment is to be shipped.

Ex:
- Air - general air cargo
- Air - next day air
- Air - overnight air
- Barge
- Fast Freight
- Piggyback Service
- Pipeline
- Rail
- Ship
- Tanker
- Truck
- Transloading Privilege
- Vessel

Columns.Name: ShipmentMethodId

Columns.Description: The name of a Shipment Method.

Columns.Name: ShipmentMethodDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Shipment Method.

Columns.Name: ExpressShipmentMethodIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the shipment method is considered to be an express shipment method.
